last_episode_to_air.name: Dreadtrux Part 2
last_episode_to_air.overview: With the mighty Dreadtrux threatening to destroy the crater, Ty considers working with D-Structs to save both of their homes.

name: Dinotrux
overview: Half dinosaur, half construction truck, full-on fun! Watch giant Ty Rux, his little buddy Revvit and the crew come face-to-face with evil D-Structs.

seasons.name: Season  2
seasons.overview: The Adventure continues with Ty, Revvit, and the rest of the Trux as they make New Friends, New Enemies and Face all New Challenges. With danger and mystery around every corner, these Half-Dinosaur, Half-Truck and all awesome friends will 'Trux It Up' to Build a Better World.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: As the Dinotrux continue make their community bigger and better, New Enemies come to challenge Ty, Revvit and the rest of their friends. But with bigger builds, New Dinotrux and Reptools soon to follow, these Half-Dinosaur, Half-Construction Vehicle and All Awesome friends are more determined than ever to build their way out of any situation. Let's Trux It Up!

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: The Dinotrux face the biggest and baddest challenges yet in all-new episodes of DreamWorks Dinotrux! When D-Structs teams with other villains, Splitter, Blayde, and Pounder, the Dinotrux must enlist the community and use their smartest builds to keep the crater safe! But after an even more enormous threat comes to the crater, Ty & D-Structs must put their differences aside and work together!

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview: From the sea to the desert, the brave and generous Dinotrux travel far and wide to meet new friends and enemies, including the fearsome Dreadtrux.

episodes.name: Ty and Revvit
episodes.overview: Meet Ty Rux and his buddy Revvit as they join forces with the giant Dinotrux team that are half dinosaur, half construction truck anf full-on fun!

episodes.name: Scrapadactyls
episodes.overview: When Revvit and his Reptool friends wander out of their ravine, the Dinotrux must save them from a flock of wild Scrapadactyls.

episodes.name: Garage
episodes.overview: The Dinotrux build a garage to keep the Reptools safe, but D-Structs tries to ruin their plans by turning the friends against each other.

episodes.name: Scraptors
episodes.overview: Ty rux leads the Dinotrux on a nighttime raid to save Ton-Ton, who's been snatched by a pack of Scraptors and taken to their hive in Scraptor Valley.

episodes.name: Pit
episodes.overview: D-Structs traps the Dinotrux in a deep sinkhole -- but he forgets about tiny Revvit, who comes up with a plan to help his much-bigger friends.

episodes.name: Garby
episodes.overview: Just as Ty Rux welcomes a loud and smelly Stegarbasaurus to the crater, Revvit disappears and the gang sets out on a dangerous rescue mission.

episodes.name: Desert
episodes.overview: Under orders from D-Structs, Skrap-it steals one of Garby's parts, sending the Dinotrux on a trek through the desert to find help for their friend.

episodes.name: Schildtools
episodes.overview: The Dinotrux find a nest of Tortool eggs. The hatchlings think Dozer is their mother and start causing chaos, painting everything in sight.

episodes.name: Sandstorm
episodes.overview: The Dinotrux get caught in a powerful sandstorm that stops them in their tracks. Ty Rux and the Reptools must find a way to save them.

episodes.name: Fake Ravine
episodes.overview: When the Dinotrux settle together in the crater, D-Structs decides to go after their most important resource: the Reptools.

episodes.name: New Tail
episodes.overview: D-Structs loses his wrecking ball tail and wants to prove he’s still dangerous, but when he gets stuck the crew must decide if they will save him.

episodes.name: Ottos
episodes.overview: D-Structs loses his wrecking ball tail and wants to prove he’s still dangerous, but when he gets stuck the crew must decide if they will save him.

episodes.name: Night
episodes.overview: The crew uses Lightning Bitbugs to light up the garage when Dozer needs a late-night repair, but need a new plan after Scrapadactyls attack.

episodes.name: Rollodons
episodes.overview: When tar fills the cracks of the crater, the Dinotrux must find a way to herd the free-roaming Rollodons to help smooth over the sticky situation.

episodes.name: Lair
episodes.overview: D-Structs kidnaps Revvit to show the crew who’s boss when they compete over construction, so Ty plans the perfect heist to rescue their friend.

episodes.name: Battering Ram
episodes.overview: When parts go missing from the garage, Ace and Skya solve the mystery when they discover D-Structs has a new claw tail which they put to the test.

episodes.name: Racetrack
episodes.overview: Ton-Ton’s friends, The 'Dumps, visit the Flatirons but are too wild and crazy for the crew, so the Dinotrux build a racetrack perfect for joyriding.

episodes.name: Gluphosaurs
episodes.overview: When D-Structs tricks the Gluphosaurs into attacking the Dinotrux, Revvit must befriend them and find a way to “unstick” the crew from one another.

episodes.name: Towaconstrictors
episodes.overview: Revvit maps a path to a magical forest where the Dinotrux can explore and have fun, but once they arrive the crew is startled by Towaconstrictors.

episodes.name: Desert Scraptors
episodes.overview: When the Desert Scraptors mistakenly think Click-Clack is their leader, D-Structs’ plan to have them attack Ty and the crew is derailed.

episodes.name: Water
episodes.overview: The Dinotrux crew builds an aqueduct to bring water back to the Flatirons during a drought, but D-Structs tries to sabotage their plan.

episodes.name: Wind
episodes.overview: A fierce windstorm traps the gang inside the garage and they have fun together all night, but once the food runs out they team up to find a way out.

episodes.name: Lightning
episodes.overview: When Skrap-It gets struck by lightning, he’s suddenly smart and comes up with a plan for D-Structs to remove the Dinotrux from the crater for good.

2.name: Season  2
2.overview: The Adventure continues with Ty, Revvit, and the rest of the Trux as they make New Friends, New Enemies and Face all New Challenges. With danger and mystery around every corner, these Half-Dinosaur, Half-Truck and all awesome friends will 'Trux It Up' to Build a Better World.

episodes.name: Slide
episodes.overview: Ton-Ton wants the Dinotrux to build a slide. Revvit and Ty say it's impossible, but with teamwork and creativity, they might just pull it off.

episodes.name: Drillasaurs
episodes.overview: When a greedy group of Drillasaurs shows up to dig for diamonds in the crater, the Dinotrux make a deal with them. Skya pushes herself too far.

episodes.name: Volcano
episodes.overview: When a volcano eruption threatens their crater, Ty and Revvit come up with a plan to save their home as D-Structs tries to ruin their build.

episodes.name: Sawmetradon
episodes.overview: The Dinotrux work to save a band of Reptools who are under attack by an evil Sawmetradon that's going to destroy all their homes.

episodes.name: Speed
episodes.overview: When Skrap-It loosens Ty's master cylinder, Ty can't stop moving and the Dinotrux have to figure out a way to slow him down.

episodes.name: Flynt
episodes.overview: A big fire in the crater threatens the Dinotrux, so Ty has to go get help from a grumpy water-filled Hydrodon named Flynt.

episodes.name: Wings
episodes.overview: The Ottos are in danger, but the only way to reach them is to fly. The Dinotrux build some wings for Ton-Ton to complete the mission.

episodes.name: Slamtools
episodes.overview: A band of Slamtools makes a deal with D-Structs to trap the Dinotrux and steal their ore, so Garby and Click-Clack have to come to the rescue.

episodes.name: Blayde
episodes.overview: Dozer and the other Dinotrux work together to outsmart a bully named Blayde, who used to be Dozer's friend before turning evil.

episodes.name: Battle
episodes.overview: D-Structs gets a special spark bug that makes him super strong, so the Dinotrux come up with a plan to deactivate it and find their own super charger.

episodes.name: Cementasaurs
episodes.overview: Thanks to a couple of Cementasaurs, Ty is stuck and sinking in wet cement! The other Dinotrux and the Reptools have to find a way to get him out.

episodes.name: Eggs
episodes.overview: An earthquake separates a herd of Ankylodumps from their eggs, so Ton-Ton scoops them up and works with the other Dinotrux to keep them safe.

episodes.name: Pounder
episodes.overview: A Poundersaurolophus is on the loose, pounding everything in sight. The Dinotrux have to find a way to stop it from flattening them too.

episodes.name: Shockarachnids
episodes.overview: Dozer and Skya become separated from the rest of the crew and get attacked by a group of Shockarachnids, high-voltage spiders with a vicious bite.

episodes.name: Scaretrux
episodes.overview: The Reptools get trapped by Scraptors and build a Scaretrux to keep them away, but Skrap-It wants to steal the fake T-Trux to impress D-Structs.

episodes.name: Magnet Mountain
episodes.overview: The Dinotrux have been trapped inside a magnetic mountain by D-Structs, Splitter, Blayde and Pounder! Revvit helps Ty break them free.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: As the Dinotrux continue make their community bigger and better, New Enemies come to challenge Ty, Revvit and the rest of their friends. But with bigger builds, New Dinotrux and Reptools soon to follow, these Half-Dinosaur, Half-Construction Vehicle and All Awesome friends are more determined than ever to build their way out of any situation. Let's Trux It Up!

episodes.name: Pteracopters
episodes.overview: When a band of Pteracopters crash-lands in the crater, the Dinotrux help them rescue a friend who's been taken out by stealth Scrapadactyls.

episodes.name: Snowblazer
episodes.overview: While trying to get home from a snowy area north of their crater, the gang meets a lonely but helpful Trux named Snowblazer who helps them navigate.

episodes.name: Picktools
episodes.overview: When the crew gets stuck on a sheet of thin ice, they run into a group of Picktools, which appear to be trying to crack the ice around them.

episodes.name: Ton-Ton & Skrap-It
episodes.overview: After fighting gets them stuck in a dangerous situation, enemies Skrap-It and Ton-Ton must join forces to save themselves.

episodes.name: Garby's Gang
episodes.overview: Garby has to develop confidence as a leader when he's left in charge of the Flatirons while Ty and the others are stuck far away from home.

episodes.name: Gearwigs
episodes.overview: Click-Clack climbs out of his comfort zone to make sure his ideas are heard when the Dinotrux hatch a plan to stop D-Structs from stealing supplies.

episodes.name: Bridge
episodes.overview: A group of Trux displaced by a volcano comes to Ty for help, and the gang has to work together to build a bridge to welcome their new guests.

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: The Dinotrux face the biggest and baddest challenges yet in all-new episodes of DreamWorks Dinotrux! When D-Structs teams with other villains, Splitter, Blayde, and Pounder, the Dinotrux must enlist the community and use their smartest builds to keep the crater safe! But after an even more enormous threat comes to the crater, Ty & D-Structs must put their differences aside and work together!

episodes.name: Imposter
episodes.overview: Ty has trouble keeping all of the new Trux organized and cooperative, and D-Structs comes up with a plan that throws the crater into even more chaos.

episodes.name: Aquadon
episodes.overview: To escape big trouble, the Dinotrux quickly put together a raft and hit the sea. But there might be danger lurking in the water, too.

episodes.name: The Return
episodes.overview: The Dinotrux return to the crater from their travels to find that D-Structs has taken over and built a huge wall to keep them out.

episodes.name: Junktool
episodes.overview: When the crew is forced to spend a night in the desert to avoid a sandstorm, they wake up the next day without their most important parts.

episodes.name: Dreadtrux Part 1
episodes.overview: The Dinotrux investigate when all of the other trux in the crater start running away from a mysterious mountain that may be coming alive.

episodes.name: Dreadtrux Part 2
episodes.overview: With the mighty Dreadtrux threatening to destroy the crater, Ty considers working with D-Structs to save both of their homes.

5.name: Season 5
5.overview: From the sea to the desert, the brave and generous Dinotrux travel far and wide to meet new friends and enemies, including the fearsome Dreadtrux.
